  +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  | _address_proto| ..._prefixlen |     sadb_address_reserved     |
  +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  ~         selector source address (64-bit aligned sockaddr)     ~
 >+---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  |       sadb_address_len        |     sadb_address_exttype      |
  +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  | _address_proto| ..._prefixlen |     sadb_address_reserved     |
  +---------------+---------------+---------------+---------------+
  ~     selector destination address (64-bit aligned sockaddr)    ~
